HEADWORD: oil spill
<hw>oil" spill`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A layer of oil floating on water
or covering the shoreline of a body of water; -- usually petroleum which
has leaked from an oil tanker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

